headline: HP Contributes to Trump Inaugural Fund With Tariff Risk Looming
summary: (Bloomberg) -- HP Inc. is making a contribution to Donald Trump’s inauguration, joining Microsoft Corp., Amazon.com Inc. and other major technology companies funding festivities this month for the incoming US president who has vowed to impose sweeping tariffs.
